      "value": "<p>Starting at 15th level, you can discorporate into your swarm, avoiding danger. When you take damage, you can use your reaction to give yourself resistance to that damage. You vanish into your swarm and then teleport to an unoccupied space that you can see within 30 feet of you, where you reappear with the swarm.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you can't do so again until you complete a short or long rest.</p>",
